{"type": "article", "id": 21974, "title": "大理石花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135014yebtivFhOkNX4UJV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">意大利设计师 Moreno Ratti 擅长用大理石创作，这套花瓶和果盘系列来自他出身地 carrara（卡拉拉）的白色大理石。他利用了用取芯过程中的废弃材料，然后使用树脂帮助稳定，使花瓶像是悬空在玻璃里，而大理石表面细微的纹路也更清晰。彩色的花朵或糖果放置其中，在庄重典雅的大理石对比下能更突显。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135012Jw2DZQhF9PYj3RUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135013TwFPsX7KOlW6uHRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135013z5flBdEUD9gMpe3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135014lPzG5fW4LNpBx2un.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}